metadata.name: HARBINGER I
metadata.description:
Legend has it, that once every 10,000 years, the Crystal Nymphs come out of hiding from deep in the earth’s core, to put on the most visually spectacular performance the world has ever known.   

Unfortunately, this dance has another purpose… 

...A harbinger for the End Times - a catalyst for the cycle of death and rebirth of the earth and all living beings inhabiting it. 

--

2000x3500px
ytopp 2022
